  "texts": [
    "3D face generation 3D face generation is a popular research direction in the field of virtual human generation.",
    "In particular, researchers focus on reconstructing 3D faces from 2D images, which can mitigate the constraints on space and equipment required for tasks involved in 3D face reconstruction.",
    "3D human body generation 3D human body generation is an important subtask of 3D object reconstruction.",
    "The reconstruction of a 3D human body involves integrating the features of the body into 2D images and deforming a parametric general model of the body to generate a more refined model.",
    "The poses of models can be freely changed to match the poses in images."
